This Online Reservation System includes all the necessary fields which are required during online reservation system. This Online Reservation System will be easy to use and can be used by any person. The basic idea behind this project is to save data in a central database which can be accessed by any authorize person to get information and saves time and burden which are being faced by their customers.
It also contains login form, necessary details such as their basic details, train number, train name will automatically come in the box, class type, date of journey, from (place) to destination and after that, users will have to press Insert button and cancellation form.
